<item>
            <title>[LU-14507] &apos;lfs getdirstripe -D&apos; prints stripe count -1 as 4294967295 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14507</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs getdirstripe -D&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; on a directory that has a default stripe &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs setdirstripe -D -c -1&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; it prints the stripe count as an unsigned value:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# mkdir /mnt/testfs/dir
# lfs setdirstripe -D -c -1 /mnt/testfs/dir
# lfs getdirstripe -D /mnt/testfs/dir
lmv_stripe_count: 4294967295 lmv_stripe_offset: -1 lmv_hash_type: fnv_1a_64
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
